title: AlienGuise
description: AlienGUIse Theme Manager is powered by MyColors technology from Stardock and dramatically transforms the appearance of your Microsoft Windows operating system into a truly unique display, and features exclusive Alienware-centered skins like, Invader, Darkstar, ALXMorph, and the new Xenomorph. These sleek and stylish Alienware skins vividly alter the appearance of desktop features such as your icons, wallpaper, and Windows Media Player.
